{"tid":337073,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"［婆媳問題？］點樣對付屋企既死港女？","createTime":"2017-07-27T03:43:43.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-17T05:23:14.000Z","uid":66252,"like":6,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5d949368e7be3c3ad279a21c7df845e63ef2029d","tid":337073,"uid":66252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T03:43:43.000Z","msg":"是咁的 我有時會去男友家住 <br />\n咁佢屋企得佢呀哥 仲有佢條女<br />\n佢條女正宗死港女黎既 大聲講大聲笑 成撚日嘈住我地訓教<br />\n我同我條仔反映 佢就話始終你呀嫂黎 忍下啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但當佢地訓緊教 我用正常聲量講野（唔會嘈到人）<br />\n我條仔就會叫我用氣聲講野<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n條女成日落撚完妝 啲化妝綿就咁放係到又唔扔<br />\n我條仔幫佢扔埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢條女又成日係我地房偷野 又唔放返好<br />\n我條仔仲要幫住晒話 啲野係佢拎出黎<br />\n<br />\n最撚離譜個次<br />\n我同男朋友去日本<br />\n條女叫我地幫佢買對鞋返黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n對鞋明明香港都有仲要平啲<br />\n結果令我地趕唔上班機返黎<br />\n我嬲到仆街<br />\n我條仔：<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">唔好咁小氣啦</span><br />\n<br />\n屌 係咪真係要為左一家人既名義 <br />\n而我既感受就唔洗理呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好想趕走條死港女呀"},{"pid":"0cc4f613e6176c74df5c655e5cb64c378725f4b3","tid":337073,"uid":71257,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T03:45:58.000Z","msg":"溝埋阿哥"},{"pid":"0779cb616d4d5efae96c65d02126b4bfb27fc93a","tid":337073,"uid":107927,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T03:52:13.000Z","msg":"你條仔9成對阿嫂有意思"},{"pid":"0c3e5b59545843f4b1176ed993a72995f12775ce","tid":337073,"uid":43678,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T03:52:36.000Z","msg":"你知唔知咩叫婆媳問題<br />\n咩係婆 <br />\n咩係媳<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b21f92574ac5afe50d3877215d4ad3050b54903","tid":337073,"uid":76105,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T03:55:08.000Z","msg":"關你撚事咩 係佢老母眼中 ， 你兩個臭西港女無分別 ！未撚娶你 就去人屋企過夜，仲好意思話人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  明明自己都寄人籬下，以為自己係間屋主人咩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1966899c4c6dc642b7b586a76acc89d1c0924e65","tid":337073,"uid":17619,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T03:55:23.000Z","msg":"你係活港女？"},{"pid":"117e3999c0761b89972c88c68f6c65bef46ab4d2","tid":337073,"uid":13875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T03:55:44.000Z","msg":"樓主你角色係佢奶奶?"},{"pid":"abb9b8fc2f3563e6f5bd8fdffa510af3cf68bcab","tid":337073,"uid":76105,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T03:57:51.000Z","msg":"同埋你上去訓， 你條仔都完全唔想理你 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  講野都唔超過十句， 唔知你去黎做乜 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n  真正免費雞！ 所以收收嗲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b94c09834d5af280bfca378d88f9ca7db691f14","tid":337073,"uid":517,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T03:58:44.000Z","msg":"你諗下點樣對付你自己啦"},{"pid":"ce0369b73bf72e6acf379ce518e199c4ba538d3d","tid":337073,"uid":105678,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T04:02:16.000Z","msg":"做雞仲咁多要求<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47ed872cd099fbac9c271e8122d8fddec6a524fc","tid":337073,"uid":91620,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T04:03:01.000Z","msg":"你確定係呀嫂？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70129bef4341f6bdb11e77ce2743873e9716c93b","tid":337073,"uid":9880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T04:06:19.000Z","msg":"屋主都未出聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b4c86ee27cb0f779d7e951d87943eeccb2e5005","tid":337073,"uid":37153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T04:23:14.000Z","msg":"笑撚死 樓主有冇50?"},{"pid":"f631a7e7058d1374d038df1825a09f2ea1f8d803","tid":337073,"uid":9880,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T04:26:58.000Z","msg":"TOPIC 仲話要對付<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">屋企</span></span>既死港女<br />\n<br />\n係你屋企咩?<br />\n你同佢大家都係咁高咁大咋, 憑咩趕走人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"358572f994727960080f7b0bd7786f587ee91fd6","tid":337073,"uid":53672,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T04:30:55.000Z","msg":"你自己咪港女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0414e93dc03c557cc577e210443e201456cf656","tid":337073,"uid":11512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T04:34:24.000Z","msg":"#1<br />\n情像乳點<br />\n2 個月前<br />\n諗住一齊住可以見多啲<br />\n但點知對方都係掛住睇電視 毫無交流<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n放工返黎都係想同你傾下計啫<br />\n點知十句都唔知有冇<br />\n就連訓教個下都冇同我講過野<br />\n好唔開心好失望<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"422e4e9c3a1e99652669a3795281878e91741c90","tid":337073,"uid":111522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T04:36:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>關你撚事咩 係佢老母眼中 ， 你兩個臭西港女無分別 ！未撚娶你 就去人屋企過夜，仲好意思話人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  明明自己都寄人籬下，以為自己係間屋主人咩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n秒殺，唔記得咗樓主未過門，都唔知嘈咩"},{"pid":"4f0e161dcc99ba16419d8a9b928ee90b0153f006","tid":337073,"uid":35507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T04:36:32.000Z","msg":"人地屋企既事<br />\n你憑咩趕人走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6849b1a8c4e1b41e70e1c04e769b67d9d066c206","tid":337073,"uid":18753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T04:43:02.000Z","msg":"婆熄問題<br />\n<br />\n姐係個女係您未來奶奶<br />\n咁果條女姐係妳條仔老母<br />\n但睇年紀應該係後母，而佢男朋友姐係妳未來老爺又係妳男朋友丫哥，睇年紀應該係後父<br />\n所以應該係原老母死左，再娶左現在果個女人做後母，再夾計搞死老豆，再嫁翻比妳男朋友丫哥<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所以話晒自己老母先忍氣吞聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e7b54e16b18eefe60f427520cfb109d123d59ac","tid":337073,"uid":90820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T04:45:45.000Z","msg":"佢哋兩兄弟共用一條女<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n樓主係多出嚟阻住人嗰個<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1580ebe1ee108b53145022500d639af814b0c5f0","tid":337073,"uid":6378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T04:50:50.000Z","msg":"「我嬲到仆街」呢句好似啲乜乜page個結尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"281bac7aa8f7d202a08a5e2a0c6502a628b0ec14","tid":337073,"uid":92603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T04:56:03.000Z","msg":"唔好一齊住好似好d"},{"pid":"350e3bd1ecdaa7d46c647477308c57544f3511ab","tid":337073,"uid":64398,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T08:06:43.000Z","msg":"樓主有陣濃濃既 MK 味 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1df4d0876317f96603213eabb29e16c960c267a","tid":337073,"uid":54574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T08:11:49.